@startuml
title Gateway <-> Skill 长链接 + Gateway 集群内 Redis 定向中继

actor User
participant Miniapp
participant "Skill Server S1" as S1
participant "ALB" as ALB
participant "Gateway G2\n(skill owner gateway)" as G2
participant "Redis" as R
participant "Gateway G1\n(agent owner gateway)" as G1
participant "PC Agent" as Agent
participant "Skill Server S2\n(other skill instance)" as S2

== 1. 启动与注册 ==

S1 -> ALB: 建立 WS 长连接 /ws/internal/skill
ALB -> G2: 选中 target，升级为 WebSocket
G2 -> R: SETEX skill-owner:G2 alive ttl
G2 -> R: SUBSCRIBE skill-relay:G2
note right of G2
G2 本地可持有多条 skill 长连接，
但只选择 1 条 active link
用于 gateway -> skill 上行转发
end note

== 2. 下行：skill -> agent ==

User -> Miniapp: 发送消息
Miniapp -> S1: POST /api/skill/sessions/{id}/messages
S1 -> G2: 通过现有长连接发送 invoke(agentId, sessionId, action, payload)
G2 -> R: PUBLISH agent:{agentId}
R -> G1: deliver invoke
G1 -> Agent: WS send invoke
Agent --> G1: ack / later events

== 3. 上行：agent -> skill（G1 本地没有 skill 长连接） ==

Agent -> G1: tool_event / tool_done / tool_error / session_created

alt G1 有本地 active skill link
  G1 -> S1: 直接通过本地 active skill link 转发 GatewayMessage
else G1 没有本地 active skill link
  G1 -> R: 读取活跃 skill owner 列表
  G1 -> G1: 选定 sticky owner = G2
  G1 -> R: PUBLISH skill-relay:G2 (GatewayMessage)
  R -> G2: deliver relayed message
  G2 -> S1: 通过本地 active skill link 转发 GatewayMessage
end

== 4. skill 集群内扩散 ==

S1 -> S1: translate + persist + buffer
S1 -> R: PUBLISH session:{sessionId} (StreamMessage)
R -> S1: deliver session broadcast
R -> S2: deliver session broadcast
S1 -> Miniapp: push StreamMessage
S2 -> Miniapp: 若本实例持有该 session 的前端订阅，也可推送

== 5. 故障切换 ==

group G2 故障
  G2 -x R: 心跳停止，skill-owner:G2 过期
  Agent -> G1: 下一条 tool_event
  G1 -> R: 重新选择新的活跃 skill owner
  G1 -> R: PUBLISH skill-relay:G3
end

note over S1,S2
当前 skill-server 仍有本地内存态：
SequenceTracker / OpenCodeEventTranslator / MessagePersistenceService
所以 failover 中途切 skill 实例时，
可能影响流式 part 连续性与序列跟踪。
steady-state 最好保持 sticky。
end note
@enduml
